{{Infobox settlement | name = Berzosa del Lozoya | settlement_type = [[Municipalities of Spain|Municipality]] | official_name = <!-- if different from name --> | native_name = <!-- if different from name --> | image_skyline = | image_alt = | image_caption = | image_flag = Bandera de Berzosa de Lozoya.svg | image_shield = Escudo de Berzosa del Lozoya.svg | nickname = | motto = | image_map = Berzosa del Lozoya (Madrid) mapa.svg | map_caption = | pushpin_map = Spain | pushpin_label_position = | pushpin_map_caption = Location in Spain | subdivision_type = Country | subdivision_name = {{flag|Spain}} | subdivision_type1 = [[Autonomous communities of Spain|Autonomous community]] | subdivision_name1 = [[File:Flag of the Community of Madrid.svg|25 px]] [[Community of Madrid|Madrid]] | subdivision_type2 = [[Provinces of Spain|Province]] | subdivision_name2 = [[File:Flag of the Community of Madrid.svg|25 px]] [[Community of Madrid|Madrid]] | seat_type = <!-- [[Capital (political)|Capital]] --> | seat = | coordinates = {{coord|40|58|31|N|3|31|28|W|region:ES_type:city|display=inline,title}} | coordinates_footnotes = | elevation_m = 1094 | elevation_min_m = | elevation_max_m = | area_footnotes = | area_total_km2 = 14.3 | established_title = <!-- Founded --> | established_date = | population_footnotes = <!-- for references: use <ref> tags --> | population_total = 234 | population_as_of = 2011 | population_demonym = | population_note = | population_density_km2 = auto | blank_name_sec1 = [[Languages of Spain|Official language(s)]] | blank_info_sec1 = | timezone = [[Central European Time|CET]] | utc_offset = +1 | timezone_DST = [[Central European Summer Time|CEST]] | utc_offset_DST = +2 | postal_code_type = [[List of postal codes in Spain|Postal code]] | postal_code = 28194 | area_code_type = [[Telephone numbers in Spain|Dialing code]] | area_code = | leader_title = | leader_name = | leader_party = | website = | footnotes = }}
'''Berzosa de Lozoya''' ({{IPA-es|beɾˈθosa ðe loˈθoʝa}}) is a municipality situated in the north of the [[autonomous community]] of [[Community of Madrid|Madrid]] in central [[Spain]]. It had 234 inhabitants in 2011, covers an area of 14.3&nbsp;km² and a population density of 16.36people per km².
[[File:Ayuntamiento de Berzosa del Lozoya.jpg|thumb|left|City Hall]]
==Education== There is one nursery (public) in Berzosa del Lozoya.
