'''Birilyant''' or '''Brilliant''' ([[Azerbaijani language|Azerbaijani]]: ''Birilyant'' - meaning ''Brilliant'') is an [[Azerbaijani dances|Azerbaijani dance]] which has two different kinds. One of them is created in [[Baku]] in the years 1920-1922. Its music [[tempo]] is fast and its melody is extremely sensational. This one is performed by men. The second one is only for women. Its music is performed [[elegant]] and [[melodious]]. Its velocity is slow.{{citation needed|date=January 2011}}

